OL,3,C13-year-old boy arrested after teen
OL,4,Cdies in motorbike crash
OL,6,FA 13-year-old boy has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving after another
OL,9,Fteenager died in a motorbike crash.
OL,11,FThe boy was on a bike with another
OL,12,Fboy, aged 16, when it crashed in a
OL,13,Fginnel off Eastbourne Terrace,
OL,14,FPontefract, at 5.05pm on Monday.
OL,16,FThe older boy was thrown from the bike
OL,17,Fand died at the scene.
OL,19,FThe 13-year-old was arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,21,Fdangerous driving.
